0while%20those%20in%20Spanish%20capital%20Madrid%20were%20up%2016%25%2C%20according%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ey.com%2Fes_es%2Fstrategy-transactions%2Fthe-living-property-telescope%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEY%20property%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBarcelona%20became%20a%20short-term%20rental%20hotspot%20as%20tourists%20flocked%20to%20the%20city%3A%20The%20number%20of%20tourists%20increased%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cefg.eu%2Ffiles%2Frepository%2F20141014144126_BarcelonaDataSheet_eng.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E7.4%20million%20in%202012%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.observatoriturisme.barcelona%2Fes%2Fnoticias%2Fel-destino-barcelona-cierra-el-a%25C3%25B1o-2023-con-26-m-de-turistas-y-un-impacto-econ%25C3%25B3mico-del%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSeg%25C3%25BAn%2520los%2520c%25C3%25A1lculos%2520del%2520OTB%2C26%2520M%2520de%2520personas%2520turistas.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E15.6%20million%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Government%20officials%20have%20sparred%20with%20Airbnb%20and%20similar%20platforms%20over%20the%20years%2C%20imposing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fr-barcelona-fines-homesharing-sites-airbnb-and-homeaway-2016-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efines%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20various%20kinds%20of%20regulation%20that%20stopped%20well%20short%20of%20the%20new%20plan%20to%20not%20renew%20licenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAirbnb%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20sent%20outside%20standard%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%202023%2C%20the%20Spanish%20government%20passed%20a%20historic%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.catalannews.com%2Fbusiness%2Fitem%2Fspain-passes-new-housing-law-all-you-need-to-know%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20housing%20law%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20address%20the%20issue%2C%20which%20included%20caps%20on%20rent%20increases%2C%20price%20limi