order%2C%20says%20the%20filmmaker%20as%20he%20talks%20its%20much-awaited%20sequel%20and%20what%20makes%20the%20franchise%20still%20relevant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22RENUKA%20VYAVAHARE%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fexclusive-border-2-will-have-chest-thumping-patriotism-says-jp-dutta%2Farticleshow%2F111221667.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20Is%20Bhartruhari%20Mahtab%2C%20The%20Pro-Tem%20Speaker%20For%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBhartruhari%20Mahtab%2C%20a%20seven-time%20Member%20of%20Parliament%2C%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20pro-tem%20Speaker%20for%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20administered%20the%20oath%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MP%20from%20Cuttack.%20However%2C%20the%20Opposition%20slammed%20the%20Centre%20for%20Mr%20Mahtab's%20appointment%20as%20the%20pro-tem%20Speaker%20and%20%26quot%3Boverlooking%26quot%3B%20Kodikunnil%20Suresh%2C%20an%20eight-term%20Lok%20Sabha%20member%2C%20who%20apparently%20should%20have%20got%20the%20post%20as%20per%20the%20convention%20of%20naming%20the%20senior-most%20MP.%20They%20also%20alleged%20that%20Suresh%20was%20sidelined%20because%20%E2%80%9Che%20belongs%20to%20the%20Dalit%20community%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20Bhartruhari%20Mahtab%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Born%20in%201957%2C%20Mr%20Mahtab%20is%20the%20son%20of%20Odisha's%20first%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20late%20Harekrushna%20Mahtab.%20After%20completing%20his%20schooling%20in%20Bhadrak%2C%20he%20pursued%20a%20Bachelor%20of%20Arts%20and%20later%20a%20Master's%20Degree%20in%20English%20from%20Utkal%20University%20in%201978%2C%20according%20to%20his%20election%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20After%20being%20a%20part%20of%20the%20former%20Odisha%20chief%20minister%20Naveen%20Patnaik-led%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20for%20a%20few%20decades%2C%20Mr%20Mahtab%20severed%20ties%20with%20the%20party%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20He%20expressed%20displeasure%20over%20the%20party's%20functioning%20in%20recent%20years.%20Subsequently%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20later%20announced%20him%20as%20its%20candidate%20for%20the%20Cuttack%20seat.%20In%202024%20polls%2C%20Mr%20Mahtab%20secured%20a%20historic%20seventh%20consecutive%20term%20from%20the%20seat%2C%20defeating%20his%20former%20party%20colleague%20Santrupt%20Misra%20by%2057%2C077%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%C2%A0%20Mr%20Mahtab%20is%20a%20seven-term%20MP%20from%20the%20Cuttack%20parliamentary%20constituency%20in%20Odisha%2C%20making%20him%20one%20of%20the%20longest-serving%20parliamentarians%20in%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%2066-year-old%20has%20been%20representing%20the%20Cuttack%20seat%20in%20the%20Lower%20House%20of%20Parliament%20since%201998.%20He%20was%20on%20the%20panel%20of%20chairpersons%20in%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20The%20choice%20of%20Mr%20Mahtab%20to%20serve%20as%20the%20pro-tem%20Speaker%20comes%20after%20the%20BJP's%20resounding%20victory%20in%20Odisha%2C%20where%20the%20party%20managed%20to%20dislodge%20Mr%20Patnaik's%2024-year%20regime.%20While%20the%20saffron%20party%20bagged%2078%20seats%20and%20formed%20a%20government%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20BJP%20also%20registered%20a%20win%20on%2020%20of%20the%2021%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20During%20his%20last%20term%2C%20he%20served%20as%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Labour%2C%20Textiles%20and%20Skill%20Development.%20He%20was%20also%20appointed%20as%20the%20deputy%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Committee%20on%20Official%20Language%2C%20besides%20being%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Public%20Accounts%20Committee.%C2%A0%20Mr%20Mahtab%20also%20serves%20as%20the%20owner%20and%20editor%20of%20The%20Prajatan