shwin%20directorial.%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20reminisced%20about%20being%20approached%20for%20the%20role%20and%20took%20the%20opportunity%20to%20apologize%20to%20Prabhas%E2%80%99%20fans%20in%20anticipation%20of%20their%20characters%E2%80%99%20showdown%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkalki-2898-ad-amitabh-bachchan-apologises-to-prabhas-fans-beforehand-heres-why%2Farticleshow%2F111221019.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mamata%20Banerjee%20Upset%20Over%20Being%20Left%20Out%20During%20India-Bangladesh%20Talks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWest%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20upset%20over%20being%20left%20out%20of%20the%20consultation%20on%20key%20decisions%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20during%20the%20neighbouring%20country's%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20visit%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%20She%20is%20upset%20because%20her%20government's%20views%20on%20critical%20issues%20have%20not%20been%20taken%20into%20consideration%20before%20making%20the%20announcements%20on%20matters%20that%20impact%20West%20Bengal%20significantly%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20reasons%20for%20this%20is%20the%20Farakka%20Agreement%2C%20which%20was%20referred%20to%20in%20the%20joint%20statement.%20The%20agreement%20expires%20in%202026%2C%20and%20both%20India%20and%20Bangladesh%20have%20decided%20to%20push%20for%20its%20renewal%20during%20PM%20Sheikh%20Hasina's%20visit%20and%20address%20the%20issues%20related%20to%20the%20prevailing%20agreement.%20The%20Farakka%20Agreement%20impacts%20West%20Bengal%20to%20a%20large%20extent%2C%20and%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20sources%20have%20said%2C%20has%20expressed%20her%20displeasure%20as%20the%20state%20government's%20views%20have%20not%20been%20taken%20into%20consideration%20on%20such%20a%20crucial%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20met%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Saturday%20and%20agreed%20on%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20Joint%20Technical%20Committee%20to%20begin%20discussions%20to%20renew%20the%20Ganges%20Water%20Sharing%20Treaty%20of%201996.%20The%20Farakka%20Barrage%20is%20a%20critical%20piece%20of%20infrastructure%20in%20West%20Bengal%20where%20the%20Ganges%20flows%20into%20Bangladesh%20and%20is%20instrumental%20in%20ensuring%20that%20water%20diverts%20into%20the%20Hooghly%20River%2C%20which%20is%20critical%20for%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Kolkata%20Port%20and%20meets%20the%20water%20needs%20of%20urban%20settlements%20along%20the%20Hooghly-Bhagirathi%20river%2C%20including%20Kolkata.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20on%20the%20Teesta%20waters%20issue%20and%20the%20decision%20to%20send%20a%20technical%20team%20to%20Bangladesh%20for%20discussions%20on%20Teesta%20River%20water%20sharing%20have%20also%20upset%20Mamata%20Banerjee.%20West%20Bengal%20has%20had%20concerns%20regarding%20the%20sharing%20of%20Teesta%20waters%2C%20and%20this%20has%20been%20a%20contentious%20issue%20previously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20is%20set%20to%20visit%20China%20in%20July%2C%20and%20China%20has%20expressed%20interest%20in%20building%20the%20Teesta%20reservoir%20in%20Bangladesh.%20India%2C%20under%20its%20Neighbourhood%20First%20and%20Act%20East%20policies%2C%20aims%20to%20move%20ahead%20with%20the%20Teesta%20waters%20pact%2C%20as%20it%20has%20been%20a%20long%20pending%20bilateral%20issue%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20have%20confirmed%20to%20NDTV%20that%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20is%20likely%20to%20write%20to%20PM%20Modi%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20and%20Trinamool%20MPs%20are%20likely%20to%20raise%20the%20issue%20in%20Parliament.%20The%20TMC%20is%20also%20likely%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20INDIA%20Bloc%20allies%20for%20support%20on%20the%20issue.%20Top%20sources%20