-of-evs-124062400189_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fcentre-introduces-new-standards-aimed-to-enhance-safety-performance-of-evs-124062400189_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fcentre-introduces-new-standards-aimed-to-enhance-safety-performance-of-evs-124062400189_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Connection%20Emerges%20In%20NEET%20Paper%20Leak%20Probe%20After%20Bihar%2C%20Maharashtra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20against%20two%20Maharashtra%20school%20teachers%20for%20their%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20the%20NEET%20paper%20leak%20case.%20The%20First%20Information%20Report%20or%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Latur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanjay%20Tukaram%20Jadhav%20and%20Jalil%20Umarkhan%20Pathan%20were%20picked%20up%20by%20the%20Nanded%20Anti-Terrorist%20Squad%20(ATS)%20yesterday.%20They%20used%20to%20teach%20in%20Zilla%20Parishad%20schools%20and%20also%20run%20private%20coaching%20centres%20in%20Latur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJalil%20Umarkhan%20Pathan%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20yesterday%20after%20hours-long%20questioning%2C%20while%20Sanjay%20Tukaram%20Jadhav%20is%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20found%20admit%20cards%20and%20WhatsApp%20chats%20of%20several%20students%20on%20their%20phones.%20Both%20men%20were%20in%20regular%20contact%20with%20a%20man%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi-based%20Gangadhar%20helped%20Sanjay%20Tukaram%20Jadhav%20and%20Jalil%20Umarkhan%20Pathan%20contact%20aspirants%20willing%20to%20pay%20a%20hefty%20price%20for%20guaranteed%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20registered%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20police%20also%20names%20Gangadhar%20and%20Iranna%20Kongalwar%20-%20a%20trainer%20at%20a%20coaching%20institute%20in%20Nanded.%20The%20case%20ha