_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parliament%20Session%20To%20Begin%20Today%20Amid%20Pro-Tem%20Speaker%2C%20NEET%20Row%3A%2010%20Facts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBJP%20MP%20Bhartruhari%20Mahtab%20will%20be%20administered%20the%20oath%20as%20the%20Pro-Tem%20Speaker%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%20He%C2%A0then%20will%20call%20upon%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20take%20oath%20as%20member%20of%20the%20House.%C2%A0About%20280%20newly-elected%20MPs%20will%20take%20oath%20today%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%C2%A0parliamentarians%2C%20including%20Congress%20MP%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20will%20take%20oath%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20row%20over%20the%20appointment%20of%20seven-time%20MP%20Bhartruhari%20Mahtab%20as%20the%20Pro-Tem%20Speaker%20is%20likely%20to%20escalate.%20The%20post%20of%20Pro%20Tem%20Speaker%20-%20a%20temporary%20one%20--%20traditionally%20goes%20to%20the%20senior%20most%20member%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Congress%20-%20which%20was%20expecting%20Kodikunnil%20Suresh%2C%20a%20Dalit%20leader%20and%20an%20eight-time%20MP%20from%20Kerala%2C%20to%20be%20named%20Pro-Tem%20Speaker%C2%A0-%20has%20criticisied%20the%20BJP%20over%20the%20appointment%20of%20Mr%20Mahtab.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20will%20be%20elected%20on%20June%2026.%20Until%20a%20new%20Speaker%20is%20elected%2C%20the%20Pro-Tem%20Speaker%20presides%20over%20the%20first%20few%20sessions%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20conducts%20the%20election%20for%20the%20new%20Speaker%20and%20Deputy%20Speaker.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20expected%20to%20announce%20the%20new%20Speaker's%20name%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20two%20days%20after%20the%20first%20sitting%20of%20the%20newly%20elected%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Once%20the%20Speaker%20is%20elected%20-%20by%20a%20simple%20majority%2C%20meaning%20the%20BJP's%20pick%20is%20unlikely%20to%20fail%20-%20the%20Pro-Tem's%20post%20ceases%20to%20exist.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3