ot%3B%20takes%20a%20new%20approach%20by%20having%20clones%20of%20various%20ages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFishko%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20ahead%20of%20the%20series%20premiere%20that%20this%20was%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20to%20distance%20the%20spinoff%20from%20the%20original%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20really%20specifically%20intended%20to%20do%20something%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20Fishko%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20everybody%20felt%20like%20Tatiana%20had%20put%20in%20such%20an%20incredible%20performance%2C%20and%20nobody%20really%20wanted%20to%20do%20that%20over%20again.%20It%20was%20hard%20to%20imagine%20doing%20that%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFishko%20said%20this%20new%20concept%20allowed%20the%20writing%20team%20to%20explore%20the%20ideas%20of%20%26quot%3Bsisterhood%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bidentity%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20original%20show%20without%20repeating%20the%20same%20format.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f6a44ee4-d7de-416e-a125-d6e89654805b%5C%22%3EFishko%20said%20Tatiana%20Maslany%20doesn't%20appear%20in%20season%20one%20due%20to%20scheduling%20issues%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222611%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tatiana%20Maslany%20recently%20starred%20in%20%26quot%3BShe-Hulk%3A%20Attorney%20at%20Law.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66759d5c65f501a881811fb3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221958%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETatiana%20Maslany%20most%20recent%20credits%20include%20%26quot%3BInvincible%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BShe-Hulk%3A%20Attorney%20at%20Law%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BButterfly%20Tale.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EJC%20Olivera%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEchoes%26quot%3B%20is%20set%20in%202052%2C%2037%20years%20after%20the%20end%20of%20%26quot%3BOrphan%20Black%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20connections%20between%20the%20two%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELucy's%20creator%20is%20Kira%20Manning%20(Keeley%20Hawes)%2C%20the%20daughter%20of%20%26quot%3BOrphan%20Black%26quot%3B%20lead%20character%20Sarah%20Manning%20(Maslany).%20At%20the%20end%20of%20episode%20one%2C%20Kira%20calls%20up%20her%20%26quot%3BAunt%20Cosima%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20Sarah's%20clone%20Cosima%20Niehaus%20(also%20Maslany).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20camera%20then%20pans%20to%20pictures%20of%20several%20characters%20from%20the%20original%20show%2C%20including%20Felix%20(Jordan%20Gavaris)%20and%20Siobhan%20(Maria%20Doyle%20Kennedy).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%20for%20%26quot%3BOrphan%20Black%26quot%3B%20fans%2C%20Fishko%20confirmed%20to%20BI%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-tatiana-maslany-the-emmy-nom-who-people-say-was-robbed-2015-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaslany%3C%2Fa%3E%20won't%20appear%20in%20person%20as%20any%20of%20her%20beloved%20clone%20characters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20definitely%20thought%20about%20it%2C%20and%20we%20talked%20with%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Fishko%20said.%20%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20the%20timing%20just%20didn't%20work%20out%20because%20she%20was%20shooting%20something%20else%20right%20at%20the%20same%20time%20as%20us.%20And%20so%20it%20really%20was%20sort%20of%20a%20bad%20timing%20type%20of%20situation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%26quot%3BOrphan%20Black%3A%20Echoes%26quot%3B%20showrunner%20Anna%20Fishko%20and%20%26quot%3BOrphan%20Black%26quot%3B%20co-creator%20John%20Fawcett.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66759f1265f501a88181209e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BOrphan%20Black%3A%20Echoes%26quot%3B%20showrunner%20Anna%20Fishko%20and%20%26quot%3BOrphan%20Black%26quot%3B%20co-creator%20John%20Fawcett.%3Cp%3ERick%20Kern%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%20for%20AMC%20Networks%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFishko%20added%20that%20the%20producers%20were%20open%20to%20Maslany%20appearing%20in%20future%20seasons%20if%20the%20series%20gets%20renewed.%20She%20added%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20tricky%20balance%26quot%3B%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20many%20references%20to%20the%20original%20show%20to%20include%20without%20alienating%20new%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20really%20wanted%20new%20audience%20members%20who'd%20never%20seen%20'Orphan%20Black'%20to%20be%20able%20to%20come%20to%20this%20show%20and%20not%20feel%20lost%20or%20confused%20and%20really%20be%20able%20to%20just%20start%20fresh%20and%20follow%20the%20story%20and%20go%20on%20the%20ride%20and%20have%20fun%2C%26quot%3B%20Fishko%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20then%2C%20yeah%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20were%20putting%20things%20in%20there%20for%20the%20Clone%20Club%20and%20for%20the%20fans%20of%20the%20original%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20main%20characters%20of%20the%20original%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFishko%20said%20the%20writing%20team%20contemplated%20including%20a%20few%20fan-favorite%20characters%20in%20the%20spinoff%2C%20and%20she%20spoke%20to%20%26quot%3BOrphan%20Black%26quot%3B%20co-creator%20John%20Fawcett%20about%20what%20would%20have%20happened%20to%20these%20characters%2030%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20fun%20to%20talk%20with%20John%20Fawcett%20actually%20about%20what%20we%20could%20imagine%20had%20happened%20to%20them%20in%20the%20intervening%20time%20between%20when%20the%20first%20show%20finished%2C%20and%20this%20show%20that%20takes%20place%2030-odd%20years%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Fishko%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225db17c76-a4c6-4325-8c8c-2f69e77ac20e%5C%22%3EFishko%20said%20Ritter%20was%20the%20blueprint%20for%20the%20other%20clone%20castings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221775%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%26quot%3BOrphan%20Black%3A%20Echoes%26quot%3B%20apparent%20clones%20played%20by%20Krysten%20Ritter%20and%20Amanda%20Fix.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66759dbd40cf2af6e4f49c8e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221331%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BOrphan%20Black%3A%20Echoes%26quot%3B%20apparent%20clones%20played%20by%20Krysten%20Ritter%20and%20Amanda%20Fix.%3Cp%3ESophie%20Giraud%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fethics-of-human-cloning-scientific-progress-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20clones%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20of%20different%20ages%2C%20there%20needed%20to%20be%20synergy%20in%20their%20looks%20to%20make%20the%20story%20believable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFishko%20said%20they%20cast%20Lucy's%20part%20first%20and%20then%20decided%20what%20a%20younger%20version%20of%20that%20character%20would%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Krysten%20has%20this%20very%20kind%20of%20tough%20outer%20shell%2C%20but%20then%20there's%20always%20this%20vulnerability%20inside%20that%20you%20feel%20on%20screen%2C%26quot%3B%20Fishko%20said.%20%26quot%3BLucy's%20character%20had%20been%20through%20a%20lot%2C%20had%20learned%20to%20survive%20in%20the%20world%20on%20her%20own%20with%20no%20support%2C%20and%20then%2C%20also%20has%20this%20deep%20desire%20to%20find%20connection%20and%20family.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFishko%20said%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20search%26quot%3B%20for%20Ritter's%20young%20lookalike%2C%20and%20they%20eventually%20found%20Amanda%20Fix%2C%20who%20plays%20the%20unnamed%20clone%20teenager%20at%20the%20end%20of%20episode%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20really%20lucky%2C%26quot%3B%20Fishko%20said.%20%26quot%3BShe's%20an%20incredibly%20talented%2C%20wonderful%20performer.%20And%20then%20also%20looks%20pretty%20close%20to%20what%20a%20younger%20version%20of%20Kristen%20might%20have%20looked%20like.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENew%20episodes%20of%20%26quot%3BOrphan%20Black%3A%20Echoes%26quot%3B%20air%20on%20Sundays%20on%20AMC%20and%20BBC%20America%20and%20stream%20on%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amcplus.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAMC%2B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forphan-black-echoes-showrunner-spinoff-differences-will-tatiana-maslany-appear-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719198181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66759c5965f501a881811f23%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forphan-black-echoes-showrunner-spinoff-differences-will-tatiana-maslany-appear-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Anna%20Fishko%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20show's%20writers%20tried%20to%20bring%20back%20%26quot%3BOrphan%20Black%26quot%3B%20lead%20characters%20for%20the%20spinoff%20series.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aadekaiyero%40insider.com%20(Ayomikun%20Adekaiyero)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Forphan-black-echoes-showrunner-spinoff-differences-will-tatiana-maslany-appear-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Orphan%20Black%3A%20Echoes%E2%80%99%20Star%20Krysten%20Ritter%20on%20Her%20Character%E2%80%99s%20Mysterious%20Past%3A%20%E2%80%98She%20Is%20an%20Experiment%20Gone%20Wrong%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719198000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FOrphanBlack.MAIN_.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236040027%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22SPOILER%20ALERT%3A%20This%20post%20contains%20spoilers%20from%20the%20series%20premiere%20of%20%E2%80%9COrphan%20Black%3A%20Echoes%2C%E2%80%9D%20now%20streaming%20on%20AMC%