3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Farkansas-nurse-dies-helping-mass-shooting-victim%2Famp_articleshow%2F111217649.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20RSS%20vs%20BJP%3A%20Under%20The%20Cover%20Of%20Friendly%20Fire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm0q0422_narendra-modi-_625x300_09_June_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20easy%20to%20misread%20the%20Indian%20election%20result%20as%20enlightened%20voters%20slamming%20the%20brakes%20on%20the%20spread%20of%20Hindutva%20ideology%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%C2%A0juggernaut.%20It%20was%20perhaps%20no%20more%20than%20a%20costly%20tactical%20mistake%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20fought%20the%20elections%20with%20typical%20cockiness%20but%20uncharacteristic%20complacency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20overplayed%20its%20narrative%20hand%20and%20was%20aced%20by%20an%20opposition%20which%20capitalised%20on%20the%20unforced%20error.%20It%20helped%20that%20the%20BJP's%20hubris%20did%20not%20let%20the%20party%20correct%20the%20blunder.%20Instead%2C%20they%20kept%20betting%20on%20the%20same%20number%20for%20the%20jackpot.%20The%20party%20was%20lucky%20to%20escape%20with%20bruises%20from%20what%20many%20gleefully%20see%20as%20a%20train%20wreck%2C%20although%20a%20careful%20examination%20would%20reveal%20that%20it%20is%20barely%20scathed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Larger%20Goal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20nothing%20but%20an%20instrument%20in%20a%20much%20larger%20mission%20that%20transcends%20five-year%20election%20cycles%20and%20mortal%20leaders%2C%20their%20occasional%20delusions%20notwithstanding.%20The%20ideological%20project%20completes%20a%20century%20in%20its%20organised%20form%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20next%20year.%20The%20Hindutva%20enterprise%20is%20unhindered%20and%20deep-set.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20stray%20comments%20from%20RSS%20leaders%20about%20the%20elections.%20Indresh%20Kumar%2C%20patron%20of%20the%20Muslim%20Rashtriya%20Manch%2C%20which%20is%20ideologically%20affiliated%20to%20the%20RSS%2C%20remarked%20caustically%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20party%20that%20worshipped%20Ram%20but%20gradually%20became%20arrogant%20was%20declared%20the%20largest%20party.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20their%20arrogance%2C%20the%20votes%20and%20power%20they%20should%20have%20received%20were%20withheld%20by%20God%E2%80%9D.%20It%20may%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20rebuke%20to%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20but%20despite%20Kumar%20being%20a%20member%20of%20the%20RSS%20national%20executive%2C%20it%20does%20not%20mean%20much%20as%20he%20has%20no%20publicly%20known%20responsibility%20vis%20a%20vis%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20analysis%20of%20the%20BJP's%20muted%20show%20by%C2%A0Ratan%20Sharda%20in%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20mouthpiece%C2%A0%3Ci%3EOrganiser%3C%2Fi%3E%C2%A0defended%20the%20RSS's%20election%20work%20and%20found%20unresponsive%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20flawed%20candidate%20selection%20as%20reasons%20for%20its%20losses.%20Sharda%20blamed%20the%20BJP%20for%20not%20espousing%20Hindu%20causes%20and%20defending%20Hindutva%20warriors%20enough.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BFast%20Fingers%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNetas%20with%20fast%20fingers%20on%20Twitter%20and%20FB%20etc%20mostly%20kept%20quiet%20on%20murders%20of%20BJP-RSS%20workers.%20The%20impression%20that%20BJP%20leadership%20does%20not%20care%20for%20its%20workers%20has%20struck%20roots.%20Is%20it%20so%20difficult%20to%20show%20sensitivity%20and%20show%20public%20support%20for%20them%3F%20People%20insulting%20Ram%20and%20Hindu%20Dharma%20get%20a%20red%20carpet%20welcome%20but%20a%20young%20seasoned%20Nupur%20Sharma%20is%20scolded%20harshly%2C%20publicly.%20Though%20I%20have%20repeatedly%20said%2C%20she%20only%20quoted%20Hadis%3B%20even%20if%20she%20made%20a%20mistake%2C%20is%20this%20how%20you%20treat%20your%20frontliners%3F%20How%20does%20a%20worker%20feel%20secure%20in%20difficult%20battlefields%20like%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20or%20Kerala%3F%E2%80%9D%20This%20despite%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%C2%A0Modi's%20election%20campaign%20being%20armed%20with%20a%20sharp%20Hindutva%20edge.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20Sharda%20being%20sworn%20to%20the%20RSS%20ideology%2C%20his%20comments%20are%20not%20owned%20by%20the%20organisation.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20much%20stronger%20criticism%20of%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20from%20organisational%20stalwarts%20such%20as%20the%20late%20MG%20Vaidya%2C%20were%20dismissed%20by%20the%20RSS%20as%20independent%20opinion.%20That%2C%20however%2C%20is%20not%20the%20case%20with%20Sarsanghachalak%20Mohan%20Bhagwat.%20His%20words%20are%20as%20official%20as%20they%20get.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20avuncular%20advice%20on%20decorum%20in%20politics%2C%20Bhagwat%20said%20that%20the%20opposition%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20adversary.%20Saying%20that%20the%20opposition%20views%20must%20also%20be%20acknowledged%2C%20Bhagwat%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20are%20two%20sides%3B%20while%20one%20might%20call%20it%20the%20opposing%20side%2C%20I%20prefer%20to%20call%20it%20the%20counter%20view.%20They%20are%20not%20opponents%20and%20should%20not%20be%20regarded%20as%20such.%20They%20are%20highlighting%20one%20aspect%20of%20an%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiscontent%20Within%20The%20Family%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20politics%20has%20certainly%20plumbed%20the%20depths%20of%20malice%20and%20skullduggery%2C%20but%20is%20Bhagwat%20really%20hoping%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20pay%20heed%20to%20the%20Congress%20Party%20or%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20views%3F%20Or%20is%20it%20a%20signal%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20the%20opposition%20within%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20Parivar%20affiliates%20such%20as%20the%20labour%20union%2C%20Bharatiya%20Mazdoor%20Sangh%20(BMS)%2C%20farmers'%20body%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Sangh%20(BKS)%2C%20and%20the%20Swadeshi%20Jagran%20Manch%20(SJM)%20had%20been%20consigned%20to%20oblivion%20on%20policy-making%20and%20legislation.%20There%20was%20considerable%20disquiet%20within%20the%20family%20over%20the%20contempt%20shown%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20for%20its%20affiliates'%20views%20on%20national%20policy.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllowing%20one's%20own%20on%20the%20debating%20table%20is%20not%20only%20courtesy%20but%20also%20an%20effective%20political%20strategy%20of%20defining%20the%20opposition.%20RSS%20affiliates%20have%20frequently%20occupied%20the%20opposition%20space%20in%20BJP%20regimes.%20The%20Atal%20Behari%20Vajpayee%20government's%20most%20acerbic%20adversary%20was%20not%20Sharad%20Pawar%20or%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20but%20Dattopant%20Thengadi%2C%20then%20the%20patron%20of%20BMS%2C%20BKS%20and%20SJM.%20Thengadi%20famously%20described%20Vajpayee%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cpetty%20politician%20playing%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20his%20policy%20advisors%20with%20doubtful%20credentials%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20days%20of%20the%20Modi%20regime%2C%20industry%20was%20high%20on%20the%20government's%20agenda%20and%20business%20leaders%20received%20the%20red-carpet%20treatment%20in%20Delhi.%20Organisations%20such%20as%20the%20SJM%2C%20BMS%2C%20and%20BKS%20felt%20left%20out%20of%20policy%20debates%20and%20complained%20to%20the%20RSS%20top%20brass.%20In%20his%20annual%20speech%20on%20the%202014%20Vijaya%20Dashami%20day%E2%80%94the%20RSS'%20founding%20day%E2%80%94Mohan%20Bhagwat%20interceded%2C%20obliquely.%20%E2%80%9CIndividuals%20and%20organisations%20who%20are%20engaged%20in%20giving%20direction%20to%20the%20society%20and%20solving%20its%20various%20problems%20must%20remain%20active%20and%20vigilant.%20In%20a%20democratic%20system%2C%20the%20governments%20gain%20tremendously%20from%20that%20activism%2C%20awareness%20and%20maturity%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20nation%20and%20it%20also%20protects%20the%20nation%20from%20%5Bthe%5D%20possibility%20of%20detracting%20in%20the%20game%20of%20power%20politics.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20did%20engage%20more%20deeply%20with%20Sangh%20organisations%20after%20that%2C%20involving%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20BMS%20in%20the%20drafting%20of%20the%20labour%20codes%20and%20SJM%20on%20e-commerce%20policy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EABVP%20On%20Entrance%20Exams%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhagwat's%20June%2011%20speech%20echoed%20the%20high%20democratic%20principles%20articulated%20in%20the%202014%20lecture%20and%20may%20have%20had%20a%20similar%20result.%20For%20starters%2C%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20(ABVP)%2C%20the%20RSS's%20student%20affiliate%20that%20predates%20the%20BJP%20by%20more%20than%20three%20decades%20but%20has%20been%20in%20thrall%20to%20the%20party%2C%20has%20criticised%20the%20government%20for%20messing%20up%20entrance%20examinations%20for%20professional%20courses.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20people%20ask%20questions%2C%20the%20government%20must%20answer%2C%E2%80%9D%20ABVP%20national%20general%20secretary%20Yagywalkya%20Shukla%20said.%20He%20said%20there%20was%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency's%20(NTA)%20credibility.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20barbs%20were%20unthinkable%20before%20the%20elections.%20With%20BJP's%20brute%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20it%20was%20also%20not%20needed.%20With%20the%20Congress%20Party%20and%20allies%20regaining%20numbers%20in%20Parliament%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20deny%20them%20as%20much%20space%20as%20possible%20in%20public%20discourse.%20It's%20like%20friendly%20fire%20providing%20cover%20from%20enemy%20guns.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20RSS%20is%20holding%20meetings%20countrywide%2C%20collecting%20feedback%20and%20grassroots-level%20analysis%20to%20be%20synthesised%20by%20the%20leadership%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20months%20to%20prepare%20plans%20for%20the%20next%20year%2C%20including%20for%20crucial%20state%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Dinesh%20Narayanan%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20journalist%20and%20author%20of%20The%20RSS%20And%20The%20Making%20Of%20The%20Deep%20Nation.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719196860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm0q0422_narendra-modi-_625x300_09_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frss-vs-bjp-under-the-cover-of-friendly-fire-5955881%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20is%20nothing%20but%20an%20instrument%20in%20a%20much%20larger%20mission%20that%20transcends%20five-year%20election%20cycles%20and%20mortal%20leaders%2C%20their%20occasional%20delusions%20notwithstanding.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frss-vs-bjp-under-the-cover-of-friendly-fire-5955881%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frss-vs-bjp-under-the-cover-of-friendly-fire-5955881%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Frss-vs-bjp-under-the-cover-of-friendly-fire-5955881%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22T20%20World%20Cup%3A%20Payback%20time%20for%20India%20against%20Australia%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719196766000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111217521%2Cimgsize-69056.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Ft20-world-cup-payback-time-for-india-against-australia%2Farticleshow%2F111217588.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20have%20a%20chance%20to%20avenge%20their%20defeat%20in%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20final%20against%20Australia%20in%20St%20Lucia%2C%20a%20small%20island%20surrounded%20by%20the%20Caribbean%20Sea%2C%20where%20fans%20are%20eager%20for%20redemption.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22DWAIPAYAN%20DATTA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Ft20-world-cup-payback-time-for-india-against-australia%2Farticleshow%2F111217588.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gunmen%20Attack%20Churches%2C%20Synagogues%20In%20Russia%3B%20Cops%2C%20Priest%20Among%2015%20Killed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2015%20people%2C%20including%20policemen%20and%20a%20priest%2C%20were%20killed%20and%20several%20others%20injured%20after%20unidentified%20gunmen%20opened%20fire%20at%20synagogues%2C%20churches%2C%20and%20a%20police%20post%20in%20Russia's%20North%20Caucasus%20region%20of%20Dagestan%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20region's%20governor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20simultaneous%20attacks%20occurred%20in%20Dagestan's%20largest%20city%20of%20Makhachkala%20and%20in%20the%20coastal%20city%20of%20Derbent%20with%20Governor%20Sergei%20Melikov%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20attack%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%20the%20police%20personnel%20had%20killed%20four%20gunmen%20in%20Makhachkala%20and%20two%20in%20Derbent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMelikov%20said%20that%20among%20the%20dead%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20police%20officers%2C%20were%20several%20civilians%2C%20including%20an%20Orthodox%20priest%20who%20had%20worked%20in%20Derbent%20for%20more%20than%2040%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20evening%20in%20Derbent%20and%20Makhachkala%20unknown%20(attackers)%20made%20attempts%20to%20destabilise%20the%20situation%20in%20society%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0Melikov%20wrote%20on%20Telegram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20know%20who%20is%20behind%20these%20terrorist%20attacks%20and%20what%20objective%20they%20are%20pursuing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20later%2C%20without%20specifying%20but%20referring%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbrazil-china-call-for-russia-ukraine-peace-talks-with-both-countries-5732561%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERussia-Ukraine%20war%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20must%20understand%20that%20war%20comes%20to%20our%20homes%20too.%20We%20felt%20it%2C%20but%20today%20we%20face%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMelikov%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bactive%20phase%26quot%3B%20of%20operations%20in%20Derbent%20and%20Makhachkala%20had%20ended%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bsix%20bandits%20have%20been%20liquidated%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20authorities%20will%20try%20to%20find%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20members%20of%20these%20sleeper%20cells%20who%20prepared%20(the%20attacks)%20and%20who%20were%20prepared%2C%20including%20abroad%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20June%2024-26%20have%20been%20declared%20days%20of%20mourning%20in%20Dagestan%2C%20with%20flags%20lowered%20to%20half-staff%20and%20all%20entertainment%20events%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20Investigative%20Committee%20said%20it%20had%20opened%20criminal%20probes%20over%20%26quot%3Bacts%20of%20terror%26quot%3B%20in%20Dagestan.%20There%2C%20however%2C%20was%20no%20immediate%20claim%20of%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia's%20state%20media%20cited%20law%20enforcement%20as%20saying%20that%20among%20the%20attackers%20had%20been%20two%20sons%20of%20the%20head%20of%20central%20Dagestan's%20Sergokala%20district%2C%20who%20had%20been%20detained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Derbent%2C%20authorities%20were%20quoted%20as%20saying%20that%20both%20the%20synagogue%20and%20church%20were%20set%20on%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20comes%20three%20months%20after%20145%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20an%20attack%20claimed%20by%20the%20Islamic%20State%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Frussia-accuses-ukraine-of-direct-involvement-in-deadly-concert-hall-attack-5734004%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcert%20hall%20near%20Moscow%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Russia's%20worst%20terrorist%20attack%20in%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719196620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fuu4qbcsg_russia-attack_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdagestan-shooting-attack-in-makhachkala-derbent-over-15-people-including-cops-and-priest-killed-by-gunmen-in-russia-5955818%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22More%20than%2015%20people%2C%20including%20policemen%20and%20a%20priest%2C%20were%20killed%20and%20several%20others%20injured%20after%20unidentified%20gunmen%20opened%20fire%20at%20a%20synagogue%2C%20a%20church%2C%20and%20a%20police%20post%20in%20Russia's%20North%20Caucasus%20region%20of%20Dagestan%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdagestan-shooting-attack-in-makhachkala-derbent-over-15-people-including-cops-and-priest-killed-by-gunmen-in-russia-5955818%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdagestan-shooting-attack-in-makhachkala-derbent-over-15-people-including-cops-and-priest-killed-by-gunmen-in-russia-5955818%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdagestan-shooting-attack-in-makhachkala-derbent-over-15-people-including-cops-and-priest-killed-by-gunmen-in-russia-5955818%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Old%20man%20can't%20even%20...'%3A%20Trump%20mocked%20for%20'empty%20seats'%