team%20if%20they%20don't%20perform%20in%20the%202025%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20the%20question%20remains%20if%20the%20players%20will%20continue%20to%20play%20red%20ball%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20and%20Rohit's%20future%20has%20already%20been%20uncertain%2C%20and%20with%20Gambhir's%20name%20linked%20with%20the%20India%20head%20coach%20job%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20a%20big%20surprise%20that%20the%20two%20veterans%20could%20be%20overlooked%20for%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20also%20worth%20noting%20that%20India%20could%20feature%20in%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20next%20year.%20There%20could%20be%20a%20possibility%20of%20them%20getting%20dropped%20if%20India%20don't%20win%20the%20Test%20mace%20next%20time%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20lost%20the%20last%20two%20World%20Test%20Championship%20finals%20to%20New%20Zealand%20(2021)%20and%20Australia%20(2023)%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719195600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fp8nlq3ug_virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-gautam-gambhir_625x300_23_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-sets-bold-virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-champions-trophy-condition-for-india-coach-job-report-5953515%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gautam%20Gambhir%20was%20interviewed%20last%20week%20by%20BCCI's%20Cricket%20Advisory%20Committee%20(CAC)%20after%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20the%20former%20India%20opener%20was%20the%20only%20candidate%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20head%20coach%20job.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-sets-bold-virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-champions-trophy-condition-for-india-coach-job-report-5953515%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fgautam-gambhir-sets-bold-virat-kohli-rohit-sharma-champions-trophy-condition-for-india-co