0his%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEammon%20Jacobs%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EPhia%20Saban's%20performance%20during%20that%20procession%20scene%20is%20so%20haunting.%20She's%20doing%20so%20much%20without%20needing%20to%20wail%20lines%20of%20over-the-top%20predictable%20dialogue.%20It's%20clear%20that%20Helaena%20is%20tapping%20into%20%3Cem%3Esomething%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebigger%20too%2C%20just%20with%20the%20focus%20on%20the%20seeds%2Fleaves%20blowing%20in%20the%20wind%20and%20her%20frantic%20facial%20expressions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAyomikun%20Adekaiyero%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20series%20does%20a%20great%20job%20of%20showing%20how%20this%20toxic%20masculinity%20among%20the%20men%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20Aegon%2C%20Daemon%2C%20and%20Criston%20%E2%80%94%20escalates%20this%20conflict.%20Aegon%20doesn't%20really%20care%20about%20Jaehaerys%3B%20he%20is%20terrified%20at%20looking%20weak%2C%20which%20also%20isn't%20his%20fault%2C%20considering%20he%20has%20been%20raised%20to%20be%20this%20great%20king.%20Tom%20Glynn-Carney%20really%20has%20one%20of%20the%20best%20performances%20in%20this%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20the%20toxic%20masculinity%20point%2C%20it's%20interesting%20to%20see%20how%20the%20harm%20of%20this%20conflict%20so%20far%20is%20mostly%20affecting%20the%20women.%20Rhaenyra%20is%20blamed%20for%20a%20murder%20she%20didn't%20order%2C%20Alicent%20and%20Helaena%20are%20forced%20to%20perform%20for%20the%20royal%20family%20during%20their%20grief%20while%20the%20men%20plot%20and%20create%20more%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20is%20also%20really%20the%20moment%20where%20we%20realize%20how%20much%20of%20a%20curse%20Helaena%20being%20a%20dreamer%20is.%20She%20can%20foreshadow%20the%20death%20of%20her%20own%20son%2C%20but%20she%20doesn't%20realize%20it%20and%20can't%20prevent%20it.%20The%20entire%20funeral%20procession%20should%20also%20satiate%20everyone%20who%20didn't%20think%20the%20death%20was%20horrifying%20enough%20%E2%80%94%20I%20think%20seeing%20little%20Jaehaerys%2C%20with%20his%20neck%20stitched%2C%20valorized%20like%20a%20martyr%20in%20the%20streets%20is%20infinitely%20worse%20than%20whatever%20else%20we%20could%20have%20gotten%20out%20of%20Blood%20and%20Cheese.%20Phia's%20performance%20here%20heightens%20the%20entire%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaralynn%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Phia%20and%20Tom%20were%20both%20such%20standouts%20in%20this%20episode!%20The%20way%20the%20procession%20was%20staged%20and%20filmed%20was%20also%20gorgeous%20and%20so%20evocative.%20The%20closeup%20on%20little%20Jaehaerys'%20sewn-on%20head%20almost%20made%20me%20puke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20also%20want%20to%20talk%20about%20the%20conversation%20between%20Alicent%20and%20Helaena%20right%20before%20the%20funeral%20procession%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20a%20huge%20insight%20into%20Alicent%20as%20a%20mother.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20I've%20gotten%20the%20impression%20that%20the%20moments%20where%20she's%20protecting%20her%20children%20are%20also%20deep%20political%20moves%2C%20like%20when%20she%20demanded%20Lucerys'%20eye%20at%20Driftmark%20in%20season%20one.%20But%20in%20this%20moment%2C%20she%20is%20truly%20throwing%20Helaena%20to%20the%20wolves%2C%20and%20knows%20it.%20Olivia%20manages%20to%20elucidate%20this%20tension%20between%20protecting%20her%20daughter%20from%20scrutiny%20and%20making%20the%20savvy%20political%20choice%2C%20but%20obviously%2C%20we%20know%20where%20Alicent%20lands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaralynn%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I've%20never%20had%20less%20sympathy%20for%20Alicent%20than%20in%20this%20episode.%20You%20can%20see%20her%20struggling%20with%20this%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20all%20thanks%20to%20Olivia's%20meticulous%20performance%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she%20makes%20the%20wrong%20choice%20at%20literally%20every%20opportunity%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20do%20think%20that%20she%20is