ctive%20for%20me%20was%20that%20mom%20who%20saw%20her%20dead%20ratcatcher%20son%20strung%20up.%20And%20the%20dog%20giving%20that%20small%20whine%20when%20he%20saw%20Cheese%20dead!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Thank%20god%20the%20dog%20is%20safe!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAyomikun%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20hanging%20scene%20really%20highlights%20how%20much%20Aegon%20messed%20up%20more%20than%20Otto's%20tirade.%20The%20smallfolk%20don't%20really%20know%20the%20ins-and-outs%20of%20what's%20going%20on%2C%20but%20they%20know%20their%20king%20has%20just%20murdered%20the%20lowest%20of%20their%20servants%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20were%20completely%20innocent.%20They%20likely%20will%20trust%20Aegon%20less%20than%20Rhaenyra%2C%20who%20kept%20the%20conflict%20to%20just%20the%20royals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20Aegon%20is%20barely%20still%20winning%20the%20PR%20war%20because%20everyone%20thinks%20Rhaenyra%20killed%20a%20child.%20But%20yeah%2C%20ultimately%2C%20I%20agree%20with%20you%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20funny%20because%20everyone%20was%20lauding%20him%20as%20a%20wealth%20redistribution%20icon%20in%20the%20last%20episode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAegon%20giveth%20sheep.....%20he%20taketh%20away%20sheep.....%20he%20slays%20rat%20men.......%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEammon%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20do%20think%20that%20even%20in%20the%20first%20two%20episodes%2C%20the%20writers%20are%20trying%20to%20show%20the%20war%20from%20the%20smallfolk's%20perspective%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20more%20than%20%26quot%3BGame%20of%20Thrones.%26quot%3B%20We%20had%20the%20sheep%2Fdragon%20debate%20last%20week%2C%20and%20now%20we've%20got%20the%20elimination%20of%20the%20ratcatchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPalmer%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20have%20mixed%20feelings%20about%20how%20the%20series%20handles%20this%2C%20because%2C%20on%20the%20one%20hand%2C%20I%20think%20that%20it's%20hugely%20important%20for%20the%20show%20to%20contextua