th%20nature%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Steve%20was%20also%20looking%20to%20make%20a%20career%20switch%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20the%20right%20time%20for%20us%20to%20start%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20our%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we%20took%20the%20plunge.%20Looking%20back%2C%20it%20was%20a%20quick%20process%3A%20We%20made%20the%20decision%20in%20January%202022%2C%20and%20six%20months%20later%2C%20we%20were%20in%20Bali.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20possibilities%20ahead%20of%20us%20felt%20boundless%2C%20and%20we%20couldn't%20wait%20to%20explore%20new%20sides%20of%20ourselves.%20In%20hindsight%2C%20it%20took%20us%20longer%20to%20find%20our%20footing%20than%20we%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2246e43255-84e1-4099-ad26-6d94ee864a15%5C%22%3EWe%20jumped%20in%20and%20tried%20to%20learn%20how%20things%20worked%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bureaucratic%20stuff%20was%20tough%2C%20and%20we%20soon%20realized%20there%20was%20no%20how-to%20manual.%20We%20ended%20up%20learning%20everything%20the%20hard%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20we%20were%20used%20to%20having%20our%20bill%20payments%20automated.%20In%20Bali%2C%20we%20paid%20them%20in%20person%20for%20a%20few%20months%20before%20we%20finally%20learned%20how%20to%20do%20it%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20missed%20the%20convenience%20of%20our%20service%20apartment%2C%20which%20had%20an%20amazing%20gym%20and%20easy%20access%20to%20public%20transport.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Australia%2C%20it's%20easy%20to%20walk%20everywhere.%20In%20Malaysia%2C%20we%20could%20also%20jump%20into%20a%20car%2C%20but%20here%2C%20although%20it%20looks%20like%20you%20can%20walk%20to%20your%20destination%2C%20there%20are%20hardly%20any%20sidewalks.%20You%20have%20to%20hop%20on%20a%20motorbike%20to%20get%20around%2C%20and%20it%20took%20us%2010%20months%20before%20we%20could%20get%20our%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20challenges%20we%20faced%20trying%20to%20get%20used%20to%20our%20new%20lives%20started%20adding%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20even%20had%20health%20concerns%20because%20mold%20was%20growing%20in%20the%20house%20we%20leased.%20After%20three%20doctor%20visits%20and%20one%20hospital%20visit%2C%20we%20had%20to%20travel%20back%20to%20KL%20before%20we%20finally%20got%20a%20diagnosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20surrounded%20by%20overwhelming%20change%20daily%20was%20draining%20and%20distracted%20us%20from%20enjoying%20the%20process.%20It%20didn't%20help%20that%20we%20were%20our%20own%20biggest%20critics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aaa550ef-34db-4742-a67f-ee257b53d022%5C%22%3EWe%20didn't%20celebrate%20ourselves%20enough%20for%20the%20milestones%20we%20achieved%20during%20our%20move%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20we%20were%20too%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efocused%20on%20getting%20our%20lives%20in%20Bali%20started%20right%20away.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EQuitting%20our%20jobs%20and%20leaving%20our%20homes%20were%20huge%20risks%2C%20and%20we%20were%20determined%20to%20ensure%20that%20we'd%20made%20the%20right%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20slowly%2C%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foverrated-things-not-to-do-in-bali-i-lived-there-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20Bali%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20taught%20us%20to%20go%20with%20the%20flow%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20cities%2C%20we're%20used%20to%20efficiency%20and%20getting%20things%20done%20quickly.%20But%20here%2C%20you%20just%20have%20to%20lean%20back%20and%20allow%20things%20to%20unravel%20in%20their%20own%20time.%20Even%20the%20never-ending%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20also%20realized%20that%20we%20weren't%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20others%20I've%20spoken%20to%20in%20Bali%20are%20experiencing%20similar%20challenges%20of%20building%20a%20life%20and%20career%20here%20while%20transitioning%20from%20a%209-to-5%20schedule.%20After%20all%2C%20having%20a%20routine%20was%20a%20huge%20part%20of%20life%2