ity%20researchers%20found%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20study%20published%20in%202014%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Experimental%20Psychology.%20The%20participants%20who%20went%20for%20walks%20saw%20an%2081%25%20increase%20in%20tests%20measuring%20divergent%20thinking%2C%20a%20thought%20process%20associated%20with%20creativity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226652f3ed-5288-42dc-a785-cd332a8df80b%5C%22%3EI%20make%20use%20of%20sleepless%20nights%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20children%20are%206%20and%209%20but%20they%20still%20regularly%20wake%20me%20in%20the%20night%20for%20anything%20from%20going%20to%20the%20bathroom%20to%20throwing%20up.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20if%20I%20couldn't%20get%20back%20to%20sleep%2C%20I'd%20just%20lie%20there%2C%20restless%20and%20awake%2C%20until%20the%20alarm.%20Now%20I%20get%20up%20and%20work%20instead.%20Thanks%20to%20some%20of%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstay-at-home-mom-works-part-time-morning-routine-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epre-dawn%20wakeups%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20have%20built%20a%20website%2C%20launched%20my%20business%2C%20and%20regularly%20beat%20deadlines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20get%20me%20wrong%20%E2%80%94%20I'd%20never%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuccessful-people-who-wake-up-early-before-6-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewake%20up%20that%20early%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20purpose%2C%20but%20making%20the%20most%20of%20it%20has%20been%20productive.%20I%20usually%20get%20a%20full%20night's%20sleep%20the%20next%20night%20because%20I%20have%20to%20go%20to%20bed%20early%20to%20compensate.%20But%20it's%20not%20like%20I'm%20sacrificing%20my%20evening%20social%20life%20because%20I%20don't%20have%20one%20as%20a%20single%20mother%20anyway.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2245b7819a-1136-4a64-92a3-2240f8eff63a%5C%22%3EI%20use%20my%20kids%20as%20inspiration%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20run%20ideas%20past%20them%2C%20and%20things%20like%20logos%20and%20my%20busine