%3E.%20I%20even%20went%20on%20to%20get%20a%20masters%20in%20the%20same%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Neenu%20was%20among%20her%20peers%20who%20were%20passionate%20about%20engineering%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20she%20was%20a%20misfit%20in%20the%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20how%20I%20was%20not%20here%20because%20of%20my%20passion%20but%20just%20for%20a%20degree.%20The%20crisis%20of%20not%20knowing%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20with%20my%20life%20kicked%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20even%20got%20placed%20at%20an%20MNC%20in%20the%20third%20year%20of%20my%20college%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20it%20was%20a%20period%20of%20recession%2C%20and%20the%20company%20postponed%20my%20joining%20date.%20So%2C%20I%20started%20my%20career%20as%20a%20lecturer%20in%20a%20small%20engineering%20college.%20When%20I%20began%20working%20there%2C%20I%20quickly%20realised%20that%20the%20students%20were%20extremely%20passionate%20about%20engineering.%20These%20were%20some%20of%20the%20brightest%20minds%20in%20Kerala%2C%20with%20great%20scores%20and%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20felt%20inadequate%20because%20I%20lacked%20professional%20experience%20beyond%20my%20degree%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-1-1718888498.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Neenu%20Rathin%2C%20Founder%20of%20Social%20Town.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-1-1718888498.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsocial-town-1-1