nt%20of%20small%20plastic%20bottles%20and%20large%20budgets%2C%20weddings%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F323755%2Fmothers-anupama-charulatha-swmrt-bengaluru-plastic-free-low-waste-wedding-composting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerally%20sustainable%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20weren%E2%80%99t%20they%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20have%20a%20simple%20wedding%20with%20a%20few%20guests%2C%20the%20chosen%20venue%20was%20the%20family%20farm.%20The%20next%20step%20was%20decorations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20to%20go%20local.%20We%20chose%20locally%20available%20mango%20and%20coconut%20leaves%20for%20decorations%2C%20which%20could%20be%20composted%20too.%20While%20reusable%20steel%20%3Cem%3Emantapas%3C%2Fem%3E%20are%20available%2C%20we%20chose%20to%20go%20with%20a%20sugarcane%20one%20as%20it%20is%20traditionally%20used%20and%20grows%20in%20Shivamogga.%20It%20is%20also%20something%20that%20our%20cows%20love%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Poorvi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20shared%20her%20vision%20with%20the%20decorators%2C%20they%20came%20up%20with%20more%20ideas%20and%20were%20excited%20about%20not%20using%20plastic.%20They%20ensured%20that%20the%20aesthetics%20weren%E2%80%99t%20compromised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20and%20biggest%20step%20was%20catering%2C%20where%20most%20of%20the%20waste%20is%20generated%20during%20weddings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6d2_KetPkV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC6d2_KetPkV%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdi